cc:Work.dc:description: The Gonzago Framework logo showing a skull with a crown in reference to The Murder of Gonzago, a play within The Tragedy of Hamlet, Prince of Denmark. It is next to the Gonzago Framework word mark. The elements of the logo have been separated.
